added.description: In an effort to help Megan, Eric gets a job as a big boy bus driver. When he hits rough waters, it's up to the Beef Boys to get him out.
added.title: Bus Driver

added.description: Asta and Yuno, two orphans living in the small Hage Village, share a dream—to become the Wizard King! But in this world of magic, Asta is powerless. When the time comes for their grimoire awarding ceremony, will his luck change?
added.title: Asta and Yuno

added.description: The battles continue to heat up as Luck and Klaus prove that hard work pays off!  But in the final round of the first half, Yuno and Noelle will face Solid Silva—Noelle's brother!
added.title: Bad Blood

added.description: Not even the sickening crack of his own bones will cause Asta to fall into despair! Right when things seem the most hopeless, he pushes past his limit to keep fighting on. But is the battle finally won?
added.title: Beyond Limits

added.description: Luck and friends enlist an unusual ally in their fight against the elvish Dorothy Unsworth. Droit recalls the humans' atrocities against his people.
added.title: Humans Who Can Be Trusted

added.description: After a chance encounter with their squadmate Luck, Magna and Vanessa go to extremes in a struggle to free their friend from a crazed elf's clutches.
added.title: Lightning of Rage vs. Friends

added.description: Yami rushes to Julius's side as the Wizard King's battle with Licht draws to a close. Yuno's team approaches the center of the terrorist's hideout.
added.title: New Future

added.description: A visit to the Wizard King goes awry when Asta and the knights learn the Diamond King is attacking! The Golden Dawn keeps the attackers at bay but are the Black Bulls up for another battle after returning from the Underwater Temple?
added.title: Proof of Rightness

added.description: Gauche, Gordon, and Grey are holding down the fort when the hideout is attacked by some familiar faces. The trio must work fast to defend their home.
added.title: The Black Bulls' Hideout

added.description: Yami and Licht face off in a fierce battle of Dark and Light Magic! Meanwhile, Asta tests his new ability to sense qi to face Valtos. But is the power of two Black Bulls enough to take these powerful foes down?
added.title: The Light of Judgment

added.description: The traitor to the kingdom is called out! But is it really…?! After apprehending the traitor, Asta and Yami are given information about what the Eye of the Midnight Sun are after—and where the Black Bulls will face their next mission!
added.title: Three-Leaf Salute

added.description: Retired from werewolf hunting and running his tropical themed dream bar, Neon Joe gets an ominous visit from his past, and must resist the temptation to give in to his anger. Will he succeed?
added.title: Loose Lips Drink Sips

added.description: It is revealed that Neon Joe authored a series of erotica novels many years ago.
added.title: Neon Nights

added.description: The final showdown between Neon Joe and the Cybots.
added.title: Not Earth China

added.description: You break it, you buy it
added.title: Earth

removed.title: The Moon Masters

removed.description: Mereoleona is left to face five powerful elf enemies alone, putting her "undefeated" title to the test. Mimosa's Royal Knight teammates turn on her.
